  "id": "api/core/OnChanges",
  "title": "OnChanges",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L18-L34\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L18-L34\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/OnChanges\", \"name\": \"OnChanges\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"onchanges\">OnChanges<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#onchanges\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Lifecycle hook that is called when any data-bound property of a directive changes.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/OnChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnChanges</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#ngOnChanges\">ngOnChanges(changes: SimpleChanges): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"descendants class\">\n    <h2 id=\"class-implementations\">Class Implementations<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#class-implementations\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n\n<ul>\n  \n    <li>\n      <code><a href=\"api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">UpgradeComponent</a></code>\n      \n\n\n    </li>\n  \n</ul>\n\n\n  </div>\n  \n\n</section>\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>ngOnChanges</code> is called right after the data-bound properties have been checked and before view\nand content children are checked if at least one of them has changed.\nThe <code>changes</code> parameter contains the changed properties.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">See <a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">\"Lifecycle Hooks Guide\"</a>.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngOnChanges\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th><h3 id=\"ngonchanges\">\n    ngOnChanges()\n    \n  <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#ngonchanges\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3></th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngOnChanges(changes: <a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a>): void</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>changes</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code><a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage Notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'my-cmp', template: `...`})\nclass MyComponent implements <a href=\"api/core/OnChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnChanges</a> {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()\n  prop: number;\n\n  ngOnChanges(changes: <a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a>) {\n    // changes.prop contains the old and the new value...\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/common/NgTemplateOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/DoCheck\n - api/core/SimpleChanges\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\n - api/forms/MinLengthValidator\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/PatternValidator\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/reactive-forms\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/OnChanges#class-implementations\n - api/core/OnChanges#description\n - api/core/OnChanges#methods\n - api/core/OnChanges#ngOnChanges\n - api/core/OnChanges#ngonchanges\n - api/core/OnChanges#onchanges\n - api/core/OnChanges#usage-notes\n - api/core/SimpleChanges\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L18-L34\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L18-L34\n-->"
